  <source>University Hospital, Angers</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective randomized cross over study aims to compare nCPAP with mandibular
      advancement device for the treatment of sleep apnea syndrome.The effectiveness of nCPAP and
      oral appliance on apnea-hypopnea index, daytime sleepiness and quality of life will be
      compared in 60 patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
